  "feesApplyText": "<b>PERMITTED PAYMENTS</b> - ASSURED SHORTHOLD TENANCIES<br /><br />\r<u><b>Before the Tenancy</b></u><br /><br />\r<b>Holding Deposit</b><br />\r1 Weeks Rent<br /><br />\r<b>Security Deposit (Tenancy Deposit)</b>\rIf the agreed rent is less than \u00a350,000 per annum a deposit equivalent to five weeks rent is required. Should the agreed rent be in excess of \u00a350,000 per annum then a deposit equivalent to six weeks rent is required.<br /><br />\r<u><b>During the Tenancy</b></u><br /><br />\r<b>Variation of the Tenancy Agreement</b><br />\rIf the Tenant requests any changes to the Tenancy Agreement and the Landlord agrees to such changes, Hurford Salvi Carr reserves the right to charge up to \u00a350 to administer each variation of the Tenancy Agreement. Should our reasonable costs exceed \u00a350 we will notify the Tenant in advance.<br /><br />\r<b>Late Payment of Rent</b><br />\rHurford Salvi Carr reserves the right to charge 3% above the prevailing Bank of England base rate on any late payment of rent after 14 days have passed.<br /><br />\r<b>Replacement of Keys or Security Devices</b><br />\rShould the Tenant lose, misplace or damage any keys or security devices, Hurford Salvi Carr reserves the right to charge up to \u00a350 or all reasonably costs incurred for replacement of the keys / security devices.<br /><br />\r<b>Assignment of the Tenancy Agreement</b><br />\rShould the Landlord agree to a change of Tenant, the outgoing Tenant will be responsible for all reasonable costs incurred by Hurford Salvi Carr and/or the Landlord in consideration of administering the request.<br /><br />\r<b>Early Termination of the Tenancy</b><br />\rShould the Landlord agree to an early termination of the Tenancy, the Tenant will be responsible for any financial loss suffered by the Landlord and all reasonable costs incurred by Hurford Salvi Carr in consideration of administering the early termination.<br /><br />\r<b>TENANT PROTECTION</b><br /><br />\rHurford Salvi Carr is a member of ARLA Propertymark which is a client money protection scheme, and also a member of The Property Ombudsman which is a redress scheme. You can find out more details on our website <u>.hurford-salvi-carr.co.uk</u> or by contacting us directly.",
